                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18310217-158-victim1575 t18310217-158-viclabel954"></join>. On the 9th of February I was sitting in our parlour, and was alarmed by my dog, who heard the prisoner in the passage - I got up, opened the door, and the mat was gone; I looked out, and saw the prisoner about four doors off with the mat on his back - I pursued him, brought him back, and sent for a Police-constable - I have seen the prisoner before, but did not know him; our front door is always open, and this mat was between that and the inner door.</p>

